This is a photo of the original wiper switch. Notce there there is just a plastic pin that activates the washer valve (look for the two balck rubber washer hoses on the left side):

http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/MoreParts5/160-WasherValve.jpg

Now look at the SWF replacement switch. There is now an electrical contact above the valve:

http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/MoreParts8/42-WasherContact.jpg

